Lucent rises after contract announcement . Shares of Lucent Technologies Inc rose on Thursday in heavy trading . Shares rose 1 to 48 - 3 / 8 with over two million shares changing hands in early afternoon trading . Earlier , Lucent said it won a $ 71 million contract to supply and install a wireless network to Shinsegi Telecomm Inc , a Korean phone service providers . The network will cover the areas of Pusan and Kyungnam , which are located in the south , Lucent said , and Shinsegi plans to expand its service network to cover the entire country by the end of the year . 
